son theorem, bifurcations, and chaos. The second part of the book begins with a self-contained chapter on differential geometry that introduces notions of manifolds, mappings, vector fields, the Jacobi-Lie bracket, and differential forms.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 7aSCIENCE / Physics / Mathematical & Computational.2bisacsh1 aMaruskin, Jared M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Studies in Mathematical Physics eBook-Packagez978311064530908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chem., Mat.Sc, Geosc 2018 Englishz978311060422108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chemistry,  Materials Sc, Geosc 2018z9783110603224oZDB-23-DPC0 cEPUBz97831105980320 cprintz978311059729540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311059780640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110597806423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110597806/original  a978-3-11-060422-1  EBOOK PACKAGE Physics, Chem., Mat.Sc, Geosc 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-064530-9  DG Studies in Mathematical Physics eBook-Package  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076248-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_